and astrophysicist Jeffrey

00:28:43.810 --> 00:28:45.550 align:middle line:90%
Bennett brings it home, does he?

00:28:45.550 --> 00:28:49.140 align:middle line:10%
With his books for children,
with his books for college,

00:28:49.140 --> 00:28:52.250 align:middle line:10%
and of course, his latest,
"What is Relativity?"

00:28:52.250 --> 00:28:54.080 align:middle line:10%
all About Albert Einstein.

